@SenBooker is exactly right -- Environmental Justice is one of the defining issues of our time.

Whether it's clean drinking water, food deserts, or proximity to industrial sites - we must continue to prioritize #EJ issues across the board.
https://t.co/zkzLKgPv5g

The demands from 
@rashadrobinson &amp; @ColorOfChange to @Facebook are entirely reasonable and necessary. 

In fact, many are the same demands I have made to @Facebook https://t.co/SMKai0jDs7

It was a powerful moment to stand with my colleagues from @TheBlackCaucus to introduce the #JusticeInPolicingAct yesterday.

@HouseDemocrats are fighting for real reform. 
This is our time. https://t.co/F4CzW4OVIM
